==Cyrillic alphabet==
===Letter===
'''Њ''', '''њ''' (''italics: Њ, њ'')

#The seventeenth letter of the Serbian [[Cyrillic]] alphabet. Its name is '''њ''' (nj) and it has the sound of the English '''ny''' in ''ca'''ny'''on''. It is preceded by [[н|Н]] and followed by [[о|О]].

